		<title>U.S. Statutes at Large, Vol. 17, Chap. 24, pp. 32-33.  "An Act to set apart a certain Tract of Land lying near the Head-waters of the Yellowstone River as a public Park." [S. 392]</title>
		<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=iso-8859-1">
	<script type="text/javascript" src="https://web.archive.org/web/20130624113613js_/http://www.loc.gov/global/foresee/foresee-trigger.js"></script></head>
